+- ✅ Added visual feedback and status indicators
+
+### Capacitor Demo (New!)
+
+- ✨ Brand new React + TypeScript demo app
+- ✨ Modern component-based architecture
+- ✨ Beautiful gradient UI design
+- ✨ Type-safe AudioInput API
+- ✨ Vite for fast development
