+# AudioInput Plugin v2.0 - Capacitor Demo
+
+Modern React + TypeScript demonstration app for cordova-plugin-audioinput v2.0 with Capacitor support.
+
+## Features
+
+- React 18 + TypeScript
+- Vite for fast development
+- Capacitor 6.x integration
+- Four demo modes (Events, WebAudio, WAV, File)
+- Modern UI with CSS animations
+- Type-safe AudioInput API
+
+## Getting Started
+
+```bash
+npm install
+npm run dev              # Development
+npm run build           # Build for production
+npx cap sync            # Sync with Capacitor
+npx cap open android    # Open in Android Studio
+```
+
+## License
+
+MIT
